What is the most powerful mantra of Durga?

"Sarva Mangala Mangalye" mantra, honouring Maa Durga, is considered to be very powerful for wish-fulfilment.

What is the mantra for immediate success?

Ganesha mantra and Maa Durga mantra are considered to be very powerful for attaining immediate success.

Which mantra can solve all problems?

"Om Namah Shivaya" mantra is considered to be ideal for solving all kinds of problems.
